## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ§  NLP understanding (via spaCy)
- ğŸ”¤ Auto-corrects spelling errors
- ğŸ—ƒï¸ JSON-based local Q&A dataset
- ğŸ¤– Optional OpenAI GPT fallback
- ğŸŒ Google fallback using SerpAPI
- ğŸŒ CORS support (ready for React frontend)
- ğŸ§© Modular, extensible Flask backend

---

## ğŸ“¦ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Python, Flask, spaCy, OpenAI, SerpAPI
- **Frontend (optional):** React.js or any other
- **NLP:** spaCy `en_core_web_sm`
- **External API:** OpenAI & SerpAPI

